data.text:
Affidavit of Lucien Hubbard - NARA - 292764

Scope and content: Hubbard, a screenwriter from Los Angeles, testifies that he created the title for the film In the Days of Buffalo Bill.

Deposition of A. Brylawski - NARA - 292744

Scope and content: Brylawski, a manager of motion picture theaters in Washington, D.C., states that he exhibited a film entitled "The Adventures of Buffalo Bill."

Deposition of Fulton Brylawski - NARA - 292745

Scope and content: Brylawski researched copyrights for products bearing the name "Buffalo Bill."
